<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TRAFFIX MX – Recuperar Contraseña</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Exo+2:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/components/navbar.css">
    <style>
        /* ── Reset & Base ── */
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: #0a0a0a;
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        /* ── Animated background ── */
        .bg-layer {
            position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0;
            background:
                radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 20% 40%, rgba(245,197,24,0.07) 0%, transparent 60%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 70%, rgba(245,197,24,0.04) 0%, transparent 50%);
        }
        .scanlines {
            position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 1; pointer-events: none;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                to bottom,
                transparent 0px, transparent 3px,
                rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 3px, rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 4px
            );
        }

        /* ── Layout ── */
        .page-wrapper {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        /* ── Card ── */
        .card-panel {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 460px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(245,197,24,0.25);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 48px 40px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
        }
        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(24px); }
            to   { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
        }

        /* ── Badge ── */
        .badge-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: #f5c518;
            background: rgba(245,197,24,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(245,197,24,0.3);
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        h2 em { color: #f5c518; font-style: normal; }

        .subtitle {
            color: #888;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        /* ── Alerts ── */
        .alert-custom {
            padding: 14px 18px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .alert-success-custom {
            background: rgba(34,197,94,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.3);
            color: #4ade80;
        }
        .alert-error-custom {
            background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);
            color: #f87171;
        }
        .alert-icon { font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }

        /* ── Field ── */
        .field {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .field label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .field input {
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 15px;
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
        }
        .field input:focus {
            border-color: #f5c518;
            background: rgba(245,197,24,0.06);
        }
        .field input::placeholder { color: #555; }

        /* ── Button ── */
        .submit-btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f5c518;
            color: #0a0a0a;
            font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s, background 0.15s;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }
        .submit-btn:hover {
            background: #ffd740;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(245,197,24,0.3);
        }
        .submit-btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }

        /* ── Footer link ── */
        .back-link {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 28px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .back-link a {
            color: #f5c518;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }
        .back-link a:hover { opacity: 0.8; }

        /* ── Divider ── */
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            margin: 28px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-custom">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a href="/"
               style="background-image:url(/images/home/logo.png);background-size:contain;background-repeat:no-repeat;width:100px;height:100px;"></a>
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">TRAFFIX MX</a>
            <a href="/login" class="btn btn-warning">Iniciar Sesión</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="bg-layer"></div>
    <div class="scanlines"></div>

    <div class="page-wrapper">
        <div class="card-panel">

            <div class="badge-tag">TRAFFIX MX</div>

            <h2>¿Olvidaste tu<br><em>contraseña?</em></h2>
            <p class="subtitle">
                Ingresa el correo de tu cuenta y te enviaremos un enlace para restablecerla.
            </p>

            <!-- Mensaje de éxito -->
            <% if (typeof query !== 'undefined' && query.sent == '1') { %>
            <div class="alert-custom alert-success-custom">
                <span class="alert-icon">✓</span>
                <span>Si ese correo está registrado, recibirás un enlace en unos minutos. Revisa también tu carpeta de spam.</span>
            </div>
            <% } %>

            <!-- Mensaje de error -->
            <% if (typeof query !== 'undefined' && query.error == '1') { %>
            <div class="alert-custom alert-error-custom">
                <span class="alert-icon">✕</span>
                <span>Ocurrió un error. Intenta de nuevo.</span>
            </div>
            <% } %>

            <form action="/forgot-password" method="POST">
                <div class="field">
                    <label>Correo electrónico</label>
                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="tu@correo.com" required autofocus>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">ENVIAR ENLACE</button>
            </form>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <div class="back-link">
                ¿Ya recordaste? <a href="/login">Iniciar sesión</a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/navbar.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
